title: Tonight Show with Johnny Carson - 27th Anniversary [VHS rip]
description:
I found some old VHS tapes and decided to rip them.  I have some anniversary
episodes of the Tonight Show with Johnny Carson and Late Night with David
Letterman, as well as the 1993 MTV Music Video Awards.


This is the 27th anniversary episode of the Tonight Show with Johnny Carson, 
which aired in prime time on October 26, 1989.  The sound is kinda muffled 
and the video quality isn't great, but that is to be expected given that it 
was taped from TV almost 25 years ago.
